75const char* Mpeg_Descriptors_audio_type(int8u ID)
76{
77 switch (ID)
78 {
79 case 0x00 : return "Undefined";
80 case 0x01 : return "Clean effects";
81 case 0x02 : return "Hearing impaired";
82 case 0x03 : return "Visual impaired commentary";
83 default : return "Reserved";
84 }
85}
86
87const char* Mpeg_Descriptors_alignment_type(int8u alignment_type)
88{
89 switch (alignment_type)
90 {
91 case 0x01 : return "Slice or video access unit (Video), or sync word (Audio)";
92 case 0x02 : return "Video access unit";
93 case 0x03 : return "GOP, or SEQ";
94 case 0x04 : return "SEQ";
95 default : return "Reserved";
96 }
97}

99const char* Mpeg_Descriptors_teletext_type(int8u teletext_type)
100{
101 switch (teletext_type)
102 {
103 case 0x01 : return "Teletext";
104 case 0x02 : return "Teletext Subtitle";
105 case 0x03 : return "Teletext"; //additional information page
106 case 0x04 : return "Teletext"; //programme schedule page
107 case 0x05 : return "Teletext Subtitle"; //for hearing impaired people
108 default : return "reserved for future use";
109 }
110}

622const char* Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(int32u format_identifier)
623{
624 switch (format_identifier)

1222//***************************************************************************
1223// Buffer
1224//***************************************************************************
1225
1226//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1227void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Header_Parse()
1228{
1229 int8u descriptor_tag=0, descriptor_length=0;
1230 Get_B1 (descriptor_tag, "descriptor_tag");
1231 Get_B1 (descriptor_length, "descriptor_length");
1232
1233 //Size
1234 if (Element_Size)
1235 Header_Fill_Size(Element_Size);
1236 if (Element_Offset)
1237 Header_Fill_Size(Element_Offset);
1238 if (descriptor_length)
1239 Header_Fill_Size(descriptor_length);
1240
1241 if (Element_Size<Element_Offset+descriptor_length)
1242 {
1243 Element_WaitForMoreData();
1244 return;
1245 }
1246
1247 //Filling
1248 Header_Fill_Code(descriptor_tag, Ztring().From_Number(descriptor_tag, 16));
1249 Header_Fill_Size(2+descriptor_length);
1250}

1547//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1548void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Descriptor_02()
1549{
1550 //Parsing
1551 int8u frame_rate_code;
1552 bool multiple_frame_rate_flag, MPEG_1_only_flag;
1553 int8u profile_and_level_indication_profile=4, profile_and_level_indication_level=10, chroma_format=1;
1554 bool frame_rate_extension_flag=false;
1555 BS_Begin();
1556 Get_SB ( multiple_frame_rate_flag, "multiple_frame_rate_flag");
1557 Get_S1 (4, frame_rate_code, "frame_rate_code"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code]);
1558 Get_SB ( MPEG_1_only_flag, "MPEG_1_only_flag");
1559 Skip_SB( "constrained_parameter_flag");
1560 Skip_SB( "still_picture_flag");
1561 if (MPEG_1_only_flag==0)
1562 {
1563 Skip_SB( "profile_and_level_indication_escape");
1564 Get_S1 (3, profile_and_level_indication_profile, "profile_and_level_indication_profile"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile]);
1565 Get_S1 (4, profile_and_level_indication_level, "profile_and_level_indication_level"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]);
1566 Get_S1 (2, chroma_format, "chroma_format"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_Colorimetry_format[chroma_format]);
1567 Get_SB ( frame_rate_extension_flag, "frame_rate_extension_flag");
1568 Skip_S1(5, "reserved");
1569 }
1570 BS_End();
1571
1572 //Filling
1573 FILLING_BEGIN();
1574 switch (table_id)
1575 {
1576 case 0x02 : //program_map_section
1577 if (elementary_PID_IsValid)
1578 {
1579 if (!multiple_frame_rate_flag && !frame_rate_extension_flag && frame_rate_code)
1580 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["FrameRate"]=Ztring::ToZtring(Mpegv_frame_rate[frame_rate_code]);
1581 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format_Version"]=MPEG_1_only_flag?__T("Version 1"):__T("Version 2");
1582 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Colorimetry"]=Mpegv_Colorimetry_format[chroma_format];
1583 if (profile_and_level_indication_profile)
1584 {
1585 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format_Profile"]=Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile])+__T("@")+Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]);
1586 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Codec_Profile"]=Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_profile[profile_and_level_indication_profile])+__T("@")+Ztring().From_Local(Mpegv_profile_and_level_indication_level[profile_and_level_indication_level]);
1587 }
1588 }
1589 break;
1590 default : ;
1591 }
1592 FILLING_END();
1593}

1595//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1596void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Descriptor_03()
1597{
1598 //Parsing
1599 int8u ID, layer;
1600 bool variable_rate_audio_indicator;
1601 BS_Begin();
1602 Skip_SB( "free_format_flag");
1603 Get_S1 (1, ID, "ID"); Param_Info1(Mpega_Version[2+ID]); //Mpega_Version is with MPEG2.5 hack
1604 Get_S1 (2, layer, "layer"); Param_Info1(Mpega_Layer[layer]);
1605 Get_SB ( variable_rate_audio_indicator, "variable_rate_audio_indicator");
1606 Skip_S1(3, "reserved");
1607 BS_End();
1608
1609 FILLING_BEGIN();
1610 if (elementary_PID_IsValid)
1611 {
1612 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["BitRate_Mode"]=variable_rate_audio_indicator?__T("VBR"):__T("CBR");
1613 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Codec"]=Ztring(Mpega_Version[ID])+Ztring(Mpega_Layer[layer]);
1614 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format"]=__T("MPEG Audio");
1615 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format_Version"]=Mpega_Format_Profile_Version[ID];
1616 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format_Profile"]=Mpega_Format_Profile_Layer[layer];
1617 }
1618 FILLING_END();
1619}

1621//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1622void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Descriptor_05()
1623{
1624 //Parsing
1625 int32u format_identifier;
1626 Get_B4 (format_identifier, "format_identifier"); Element_Info1(Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(format_identifier)); Param_Info1(Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(format_identifier));
1627 if (Element_Size-Element_Offset>0)
1628 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "additional_identification_info");
1629
1630 FILLING_BEGIN();
1631 switch (table_id)
1632 {
1633 case 0x02 : //program_map_section
1634 if (elementary_PID_IsValid)
1635 {
1636 //Per PES
1637 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->registration_format_identifier=format_identifier;
1638 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["format_identifier"]=Ztring().From_CC4(format_identifier);
1639 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["format_identifier"].size()!=4)
1640 {
1641 Ztring Temp; Temp.From_Number(format_identifier, 16);
1642 if (Temp.size()<8)
1643 Temp.insert(0, 8-Temp.size(), __T('0'));
1644 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["format_identifier"]=__T("0x")+Temp;
1645 }
1646 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos_Option["format_identifier"]=__T("N NT");
1647 if (format_identifier==Elements::KLVA)
1648 {
1649 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["Format"]=__T("KLV");
1650 Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[table_id_extension].HasNotDisplayableStreams=true;
1651 }
1652 //Coherency
1653 if (stream_type==0x81 && Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->registration_format_identifier==Elements::BSSD)
1654 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->registration_format_identifier=0x00000000; //Reseting it, this combinaision is not possible but a stream has it
1655 } else {
1656 //Per program
1657 Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[table_id_extension].registration_format_identifier=format_identifier;
1658 }
1659 break;
1660 default : ;
1661 }
1662 FILLING_ELSE()
1663 switch (table_id)
1664 {
1665 case 0x02 : //program_map_section
1666 if (elementary_PID_IsValid)
1667 {
1668 //Per PES
1669 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos["format_identifier"]=__T("(INVALID)");
1670 Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos_Option["format_identifier"]=__T("N NT");
1671 } else {
1672 //Per program
1673 //do nothing
1674 }
1675 break;
1676 default : ;
1677 }
1678 FILLING_END();
1679}

1681//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1682void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Descriptor_06()

3297//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3298void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::ATSC_multiple_string_structure(Ztring &Value, const char* Name)
3299{
3300 //Parsing
3301 Ztring string;
3302 int8u number_strings, number_segments;
3303 Element_Begin1(Name);
3304 Get_B1(number_strings, "number_strings");
3305 for (int8u string_Pos=0; string_Pos<number_strings; string_Pos++)
3306 {
3307 Element_Begin1("String");
3308 int32u ISO_639_language_code;
3309 Get_C3(ISO_639_language_code, "ISO_639_language_code");
3310 Get_B1(number_segments, "number_segments");
3311 for (int8u segment_Pos=0; segment_Pos<number_segments; segment_Pos++)
3312 {
3313 Element_Begin1("Segment");
3314 Ztring segment;
3315 int8u compression_type, mode, number_bytes;
3316 Get_B1 (compression_type, "compression_type");
3317 Get_B1 (mode, "mode");
3318 Get_B1 (number_bytes, "number_bytes");
3319 switch (compression_type)
3320 {
3321 case 0x00 :
3322 switch (mode)
3323 {
3324 case 0x00 : Get_Local(number_bytes, segment, "string"); break;
3325 case 0x3F : Get_UTF16B(number_bytes, segment, "string"); break;
3326 default : Skip_XX(number_bytes, "Unknown");
3327 segment=__T("(Encoded with mode=0x")+Ztring::ToZtring(mode, 16)+__T(')');
3328 }
3329 break;
3330 default : Skip_XX(number_bytes, "(Compressed)");
3331 segment=__T("(Compressed)");
3332 }
3333 Element_End0();
3334
3335 FILLING_BEGIN();
3336 if (segment.find_first_not_of(__T("\t\n "))!=std::string::npos)
3337 string+=segment+__T(" - ");
3338 FILLING_END();
3339 }
3340
3341 FILLING_BEGIN();
3342 if (!string.empty())
3343 string.resize(string.size()-3);
3344 Ztring ISO_639_2=Ztring().From_CC3(ISO_639_language_code);
3345 const Ztring& ISO_639_1=MediaInfoLib::Config.Iso639_1_Get(ISO_639_2);
3346 Value+=(ISO_639_1.empty()?ISO_639_2:ISO_639_1)+__T(':')+string+__T(" - ");
3347 FILLING_END();
3348
3349 Element_Info1(string);
3350 Element_End1("String");
3351 }
3352
3353 if (!Value.empty())
3354 Value.resize(Value.size()-3);
3355
3356 Element_Info1(Value);
3357 Element_End0();
3358}

3360//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3361void File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Get_DVB_Text(int64u Size, Ztring &Value, const char* Info)
3362{
3363 if (Size<1)
3364 {
3365 Get_Local(Size, Value, Info);
3366 return;
3367 }
3368
3369 //Testing if there is a codepage
3370 int8u CodePage1;
3371 Peek_B1(CodePage1);
3372 if (CodePage1<0x20)
3373 {
3374 Skip_B1( "CodePage"); Param_Info1(Mpeg_Descriptors_codepage_1(CodePage1));
3375 if (CodePage1!=0x10)
3376 {
3377 Get_Local(Size-1, Value, Info);
3378 }
3379 else
3380 {
3381 if (Size<3)
3382 {
3383 Value.clear();
3384 return;
3385 }
3386 int16u CodePage2;
3387 Get_B2 (CodePage2, "CodePage2");
3388 if (CodePage2==0x02)
3389 {
3390 Get_ISO_8859_2(Size-3, Value, Info);
3391 }
3392 else //Unknown
3393 Get_Local(Size-3, Value, Info);
3394 }
3395
3396 }
3397 else
3398 Get_Local(Size, Value, Info);
3399}

3401//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3402//Modified Julian Date
3403Ztring File_Mpeg_Descriptors::Date_MJD(int16u Date_)
3404{
3405 //Calculating
3406 float64 Date=Date_;
3407 int Y2=(int)((Date-15078.2)/365.25);
3408 int M2=(int)(((Date-14956.1) - ((int)(Y2*365.25))) /30.6001);
3409 int D =(int)(Date-14956 - ((int)(Y2*365.25)) - ((int)(M2*30.6001)));
3410 int K=0;
3411 if (M2==14 || M2==15)
3412 K=1;
3413 int Y =Y2+K;
3414 int M =M2-1-K*12;
3415
3416 //Formating
3417 return Ztring::ToZtring(1900+Y)+__T("-")
3418 + (M<10?__T("0"):__T(""))+Ztring::ToZtring( M)+__T("-")
3419 + (D<10?__T("0"):__T(""))+Ztring::ToZtring( D);
3420}

3422//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
